snippet.title: 🌟 MilkyWay ~Gallaxy Adventure~ 🌟  Promotion Movie
snippet.description:
Cute mobile shooting game 🌟 Milky Way 🌟 will open Google Play!

💫 Across the collapsed Milky Way, can meteors go beyond space?

- Protect the hearts of stars from monsters!💖
- Make your own constellation in space using stars!✨

https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.Alpheratz.MilkyWay
